**Idea 1 — Spock**
- Idea: AI diagnostics tools disrupting radiology + 2nd-order hospital cost compression.
- Actionable Opportunity: Long GEHC for 9–12 months until Q4 2026 earnings.
- Underwritten Catalyst: FDA clearance of GE’s new AI imaging suite + >18% YoY revenue growth in AI segment (verifiable in 10-Q).
- Supporting Arguments: ...

