- Idea: AI agents creating entirely new "preventive health" insurance vertical.
- Actionable Opportunity: Long UNH for 12–18 months until major payers announce AI underwriting pilots.
- Underwritten Catalyst: UNH Q3 2027 earnings showing >10% medical loss ratio improvement from AI.

